nfrared">IR</a> links, have been banned at some technical universities.</li=
>
<li><b>Australia</b> =E2=80=93 policies vary from state to state.
<ul><li><b>Victoria</b> =E2=80=93 the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w=
